Package game.actions

A package including all classes related to actions that will be executed by actors.
Since:
1.0
See Also:
java.awt
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AttackAction
    Special Action for attacking other Actors.
    AttackKoopaAction
    Special Action for attacking Koopa.
    BuyAction
    BuyAction is a class that handles the buying actions of actors when they want to buy something.
    ConsumeAction
    Special Action for consuming Magical Items.
    ConsumeBottleAction
    Special Action for consuming the magical water from the bottle.
    ConsumeWaterAction
    Special Action for consuming the magical water directly from the fountain.
    DestroyShellAction
    Special Action for Destroying enemy's shell.
    FreePrincessPeachAction  
    GiveBottleAction
    Special Action for giving the bottle to the player.
    JumpAction
    JumpAction is a class that handles the jumping actions of actors to high grounds.
    PickUpCoinAction
    Action to allow coins to be picked up.
    RefillAction
    Special Action for refilling the bottle.
    SuicideAction
    Special Action for Suicide (Cleaning the Gamemap).
    TalkingAction
    Special Action for talking to other actors.
    TeleportAction
